<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ق ن ع<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤١١٦ - ق ن ع]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قنَّعَ يقنِّع، تقنِيعًا، فهو مُقَنِّع، والمفعول مُقَنَّع<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• قنَّع المرأةَ:</span> أَلْبَسَها القِناعَ <span class="c1">"كلام مقنَّع"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• قنَّعَه برأيه:</span> جعله يقتنع، أرضاه به.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>